slotlockv0.10.0.description:
SlotLock: Updated to more accurate collect/remove methods. This should hopefully reduce generation failures or possibly faster generation due to less swaps?, although weirdly it seems to have caused some more failures with local items, because logic is actually correct now???
SlotLock: Updated to use the proper autohint method added in more recent AP versions rather than my weird hacky way.
SlotLock: Added archipelago.json for AP0.7.0 support.

**Full Changelog**: https://github.com/gjgfuj/SlotLock/commits/slotlockv0.10.0

slotlockv0.3.0.description:
Initial github release
Features a client to connect with that will unlock the starting items when given, instead of push_precollected 
This is better for a variety of reasons:
- makes it work with games like Super Metroid, which don't respect push_precollected from outside them.
- Provides hint points to the slotlock slot.
- Adds a goal condition, being unlocking every slot in the multiworld.
slotlockv0.3.0.title: Slotlock v0.3.0

slotlockv0.3.2.description: Fixed minor bugs and coding issues, and added UT non-breakage (thanks qwint)
slotlockv0.3.2.title: Slotlock v0.3.2

slotlockv0.4.0.description: Added the option for bonus slots, these just contain extra items and are locked by keys. When a key is received, the client will automatically send the unlocked items out.
slotlockv0.4.0.title: Slotlock v0.4.0

slotlockv0.5.0.description: Added an option to not neccessarily send out free items immediately, instead they're sent when the world they're associated with is unlocked.
slotlockv0.5.0.title: Slotlock v0.5.0

slotlockv0.5.1.description:
- Added the ability to launch the slotlock client directly by clicking the link on the archipelago website.
- Added an option to include random starting slots.
slotlockv0.5.1.title: Slotlock 0.5.1

slotlockv0.5.2.description: Fixed issue with whitelist failing for some reason.
slotlockv0.5.2.title: Slotlock v0.5.2

slotlockv0.5.3.description: Did a bunch of internal changes, which should increase compatibility with more worlds.
slotlockv0.5.3.title: Slotlock v0.5.3

slotlockv0.5.4.description: - Removed early items from locked worlds. This drastically reduces restrictions on sphere 1, meaning that worlds generate a lot quicker and more consistently.
slotlockv0.5.4.title: Slotlock v0.5.4

slotlockv0.5.5.description:
Added ability to autohint unlock items when locks are hinted, if the slot has enough hint points.

On upstream source, with hint priorities:
This only applies to hints that are priority.
SlotLock will automatically move hints to no priority if it is for an item that is for a lock already received.
slotlockv0.5.5.title: Slotlock v0.5.5

slotlockv0.6.0.description:
Switched from pre_fill to stage_pre_fill, meaning there doesn't need to be a workaround for OoT anymore. 


Also switches any starting hints from locked worlds to an unspecified hint status on AP0.6.0. - REVERTED DUE TO BUGS.
slotlockv0.6.0.title: SlotLock v0.6.0

slotlockv0.6.1.description:
Made default options actually work.
Everything except start_inventory and item_links should now be functional on these items, though to manually specify them you will need to utilise the internal names.
Also added item and location groups:
`Slot Unlocks`: All slot unlock items
`Bonus Slot Unlocks`: All bonus slot unlock items.
`Slot Rewards`: All slot unlock reward locations.
`Bonus Slot Rewards`: All bonus slot reward locations.
slotlockv0.6.1.title: Slotlock v0.6.1

slotlockv0.6.2.description: Fixed ID mismatch. previous version creates unbeatable seeds. This one still makes broken stuff, use 0.6.0 instead.
slotlockv0.6.2.title: Slotlock v0.6.2

slotlockv0.6.3.description:
Fixed bugs, so the things now act as they should.

Universal tracker does not work right with the slotlock yaml in the folder when it has any of the default options active. Remove the slotlock yaml or remove the default options inside it to use universal tracker.
slotlockv0.6.3.title: Slotlock v0.6.3

slotlockv0.7.0.description:
- Fixed client issues.
- Improved the descriptions of various yaml options to hopefully be clearer. I welcome more feedback on descriptions.
- Renamed "number_of_unlocks" to "unlock_item_copies", and "bonus_item_dupes" to "bonus_item_copies".
slotlockv0.7.0.title: Slotlock v0.7.0

slotlockv0.7.1.description:
- Fixed item groups to actually be consistent pre-gen and post-gen.
- Added a bunch of info to the slot data for potential client use in the future.
- Added and improved autohint functionality (can now queue up things to be autohinted.)
slotlockv0.7.1.title: Slotlock v0.7.1

slotlockv0.7.2.description:
- Adds option to allow free items for starting unlocked worlds, to be a middle ground of the free starting items options. 
- Adds check to ensure that slotlock isn't locking another slotlock that locks slots. 
- Fixes issue with corrupted multidata.
slotlockv0.7.2.title: Slotlock v0.7.2

slotlockv0.8.0.description:
- Added associated worlds option. This allows you to set one world as associated with another, and place its slot unlock item to be on a free item slot of that world. Note: There has to be Nothing items in the pool in order for this to be accomplished.
- Also added admin autohints, though they can be a bit buggy at times.
slotlockv0.8.0.title: Slotlock v0.8.0

slotlockv0.8.1.description:
* Fixed Autohints, they seem to be generally solid on AP version 0.6.0, though they do not appear to function at all on 0.5.1. This is a wontfix for that version.
* Added title to window to make things easier to see.
slotlockv0.8.1.title: Slotlock v0.8.1

slotlockv0.9.0.description:
* Added location previews via entrance information for slotlock slots.
* This breaks compatibility with 0.5.1.
slotlockv0.9.0.title: Slotlock v0.9.0

v0.6.4.description: Made client a bit more robust, and reduces autohint to just one. since that is likely the easiest accessible one anyway and ensures its not a loop with Nothings in the pool
v0.6.4.title: Slotlock v0.6.4
